rw-rw-r--  1 tiny4lurv tiny4lurv   467 Mar 28 00:26 test_post.txt\n-rw-rw-r--  1 tiny4lurv tiny4lurv   550 Mar 28 00:30 test_post_improved.txt\n-rw-rw-r--  1 tiny4lurv tiny4lurv   675 Mar 28 00:41 test_post_strong.txt\ndrwxrwxr-x  3 tiny4lurv tiny4lurv  4096 Mar 28 00:21 tests\n-rwxrwxr-x  1 tiny4lurv tiny4lurv  6622 Mar 28 00:40 tinyqe.py","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775001622556}}
{"type":"message","id":"704aaaf9","parentId":"e31a3fa4","timestamp":"2026-04-01T00:00:26.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_7929f7df-f35a-443e-922d-ade3b69dbc29","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat \"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Apps/Dawn-Restore/RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md\""}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":31513,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775001626947}}
{"type":"message","id":"77a9e30d","parentId":"704aaaf9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T00:00:27.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_7929f7df-f35a-443e-922d-ade3b69dbc29","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Dawn Restore Instructions\n\n**Last updated:** 2026-03-28  \n**Purpose:** Rebuild everything on a fresh-out-of-the-box computer from scratch.\n\n---\n\n## Step 1 — Install WSL2 (Windows)\n\nOpen **PowerShell as Administrator** and run:\n\n```powershell\nwsl --install -d Ubuntu\n```\n\nRestart your computer when prompted.\n\nSet up your Ubuntu username and password when it first launches.\n\n---\n\n## Step 2 — Install Ollama\n\nOpen Ubuntu (WSL2 terminal) and run:\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh\n```\n\n**Verify:**\n```bash\nollama --version\n```\n\n**Pull your models:**\n```bash\nollama pull minimax-m2.7:cloud\nollama pull minimax-m2.5:cloud\nollama pull nemotron-3-super:cloud\nollama pull gemma3:27b-cloud\nollama pull llama3.2:3b\n```\n\n**Start Ollama:**\n```bash\nollama serve\n```\n\nKeep this running in the background (or set up as a service).\n\n---\n\n## Step 3 — Install Node.js\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_22.x | sudo -E bash -\nsudo apt-get install -y nodejs\nnode --version\nnpm --version\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 4 — Install OpenClaw\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g openclaw\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\n**Set up the gateway:**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway install\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n**Configure your token:**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set auth.token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 5 — Clone Your Git Repository\n\n```bash\ncd ~\ngit clone YOUR_GIT_REPO_URL workspace\ncd workspace\ngit pull origin main\n```\n\n*See GIT_REPO.md for the exact repository URL and branch details.*\n\n---\n\n## Step 6 — Restore Your Workspace Files\n\nCopy the backed-up files from this `Dawn-Restore/` folder into your workspace:\n\n```bash\n# Copy memory files\ncp -r Dawn-Restore/memory/ ~/workspace/\n\n# Copy workspace contents\ncp -r Dawn-Restore/workspace/* ~/workspace/\n\n# Copy OpenClaw config\ncp Dawn-Restore/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 7 — Re-authenticate WhatsApp\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channel enable whatsapp\nopenclaw channel connect whatsapp\n```\n\nScan the QR code with your phone when prompted.\n\n---\n\n## Step 8 — Install Python Dependencies (for TinyQE and RAG tools)\n\n```bash\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install -y python3 python3-pip python3-venv ffmpeg\n\n# Create a virtual environment\ncd ~/workspace\npython3 -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate\n\n# Install packages\npip install requests beautifulsoup4 lxml sentence-transformers sklearn\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 9 — Verify Everything Works\n\n```bash\n# Test OpenClaw\nopenclaw status\n\n# Test Ollama\ncurl http://localhost:11434/api/tags\n\n# Test a model\nollama run llama3.2:3b \"Hello\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 10 — Connect to Dawn\n\n```bash\nopenclaw tui\n```\n\nOr open the web UI at `http://localhost:18789`\n\n---\n\n## What's Included in This Backup\n\n| Item | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `memory/` | All memory files — long-term context, daily notes |\n| `workspace/` | Full workspace — skills, scripts, TinyQE, Nava content, RAG tools |\n| `openclaw.json` | OpenClaw config — tokens, channel settings, preferences |\n| `GIT_REPO.md` | Git repository URL, branch, and setup instructions |\n| `RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md` | This file |\n\n---\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n**Ollama not responding:**  \n```bash\nollama serve\n```\n\n**OpenClaw gateway won't start:**  \n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n**WhatsApp not connecting:**  \n```bash\nopenclaw channel disconnect whatsapp\nopenclaw channel connect whatsapp\n# Then re-scan the QR code\n```\n\n**Git clone failing:**  \nCheck GIT_REPO.md for the correct URL. You may need to set up SSH keys:\n```bash\nssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"your_email@example.com\"\ncat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub\n# Add this key to your GitHub/GitLab account\n```\n\n---\n\n*Questions? Check the OpenClaw docs at https://docs.openclaw.ai*"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"# Dawn Restore Instructions\n\n**Last updated:** 2026-03-28  \n**Purpose:** Rebuild everything on a fresh-out-of-the-box computer from scratch.\n\n---\n\n## Step 1 — Install WSL2 (Windows)\n\nOpen **PowerShell as Administrator** and run:\n\n```powershell\nwsl --install -d Ubuntu\n```\n\nRestart your computer when prompted.\n\nSet up your Ubuntu username and password when it first launches.\n\n---\n\n## Step 2 — Install Ollama\n\nOpen Ubuntu (WSL2 terminal) and run:\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh\n```\n\n**Verify:**\n```bash\nollama --version\n```\n\n**Pull your models:**\n```bash\nollama pull minimax-m2.7:cloud\nollama pull minimax-m2.5:cloud\nollama pull nemotron-3-super:cloud\nollama pull gemma3:27b-cloud\nollama pull llama3.2:3b\n```\n\n**Start Ollama:**\n```bash\nollama serve\n```\n\nKeep this running in the background (or set up as a service).\n\n---\n\n## Step 3 — Install Node.js\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_22.x | sudo -E bash -\nsudo apt-get install -y nodejs\nnode --version\nnpm --version\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 4 — Install OpenClaw\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g openclaw\nopenclaw --version\n```\n\n**Set up the gateway:**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway install\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n**Configure your token:**\n```bash\nopenclaw config set auth.token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 5 — Clone Your Git Repository\n\n```bash\ncd ~\ngit clone YOUR_GIT_REPO_URL workspace\ncd workspace\ngit pull origin main\n```\n\n*See GIT_REPO.md for the exact repository URL and branch details.*\n\n---\n\n## Step 6 — Restore Your Workspace Files\n\nCopy the backed-up files from this `Dawn-Restore/` folder into your workspace:\n\n```bash\n# Copy memory files\ncp -r Dawn-Restore/memory/ ~/workspace/\n\n# Copy workspace contents\ncp -r Dawn-Restore/workspace/* ~/workspace/\n\n# Copy OpenClaw config\ncp Dawn-Restore/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 7 — Re-authenticate WhatsApp\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channel enable whatsapp\nopenclaw channel connect whatsapp\n```\n\nScan the QR code with your phone when prompted.\n\n---\n\n## Step 8 — Install Python Dependencies (for TinyQE and RAG tools)\n\n```bash\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install -y python3 python3-pip python3-venv ffmpeg\n\n# Create a virtual environment\ncd ~/workspace\npython3 -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate\n\n# Install packages\npip install requests beautifulsoup4 lxml sentence-transformers sklearn\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 9 — Verify Everything Works\n\n```bash\n# Test OpenClaw\nopenclaw status\n\n# Test Ollama\ncurl http://localhost:11434/api/tags\n\n# Test a model\nollama run llama3.2:3b \"Hello\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 10 — Connect to Dawn\n\n```bash\nopenclaw tui\n```\n\nOr open the web UI at `http://localhost:18789`\n\n---\n\n## What's Included in This Backup\n\n| Item | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `memory/` | All memory files — long-term context, daily notes |\n| `workspace/` | Full workspace — skills, scripts, TinyQE, Nava content, RAG tools |\n| `openclaw.json` | OpenClaw config — tokens, channel settings, preferences |\n| `GIT_REPO.md` | Git repository URL, branch, and setup instructions |\n| `RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md` | This file |\n\n---\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n**Ollama not responding:**  \n```bash\nollama serve\n```\n\n**OpenClaw gateway won't start:**  \n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n**WhatsApp not connecting:**  \n```bash\nopenclaw channel disconnect whatsapp\nopenclaw channel connect whatsapp\n# Then re-scan the QR code\n```\n\n**Git clone failing:**  \nCheck GIT_REPO.md for the correct URL. You may need to set up SSH keys:\n```bash\nssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"your_email@example.com\"\ncat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub\n# Add this key to your GitHub/GitLab account\n```\n\n---\n\n*Questions? Check the OpenClaw docs at https://docs.openclaw.ai*","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775001627013}}
